name: Running of the Longhorns
description:
Roaming through a pasture to photograph an old barn I stumbled upon these Longhorns. They were beautiful and seemed to not mind me being there- at least until I lifted my camera. They chased me back to my starting point as soon as the shutter slapped.

An image from my “Adventure In Beer” series; Expired Kodak Tri-X Pan(1970) developed in beer.
